The paper discusses the efficient processing of RDF data, which is a common task in database systems (cs.DB). The paper also proposes an algorithm for subgraph pattern matching, which is a fundamental problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and graph theory (cs.DS). The paper also discusses optimization techniques, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG).
